reviewText: The Good old days good to see with all the family
Amusing! Fun to watch black & white clips. Some are in other dvd's, but all in all a good addition to my collection.
Best part was looking at the old hot rods.
ever wonder what it was like back in the 50's, how did the squares deal with not rodders and so on! buy this DVD and find out how.... unless you are a square!!!!!
